    <h1>Formic at SNAXPO 2025: Exploring Automation Solutions for CPG Manufacturers</h1>
    <div class="legal-meta">Brooklyn Kiosow, Marketing Communications Manager · Wednesday, April 2, 2025</div>
  </div>

<figure style="max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px"><img src="/articles/formic-at-snaxpo-2025/1743617389-img_8575.jpg" alt="Formic at SNAXPO 2025: Exploring Automation Solutions for CPG Manufacturers" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block" /></figure>
  <div class="legal-prose">
<p>This week, Formic headed to Orlando, Florida, for Snac International’s SNAXPO 2025. We had a robot palletizing boxes, a sales team answering questions about automating end-of-line production, and our customers’ products on display — from <a href="https://formic.co/stories/mi-rancho-makes-production-leap-with-automated-stacking-of-70-million-pounds-of-t">tortilla chips</a> to lotion. </p> <p>Additionally, Formic’s VP of Sales held a session on the Snac Bites Stage on the <a href="https://formic.co/articles/simplifying-production-automation">essential journey to successful automation</a> for CPG manufacturers. He broke down the three automation options in 2025, how robot rentals improve automation accessibility, and how to create a holistic business and deployment plan. </p> <p>He also explained the cost of waiting to automate, including increased operational costs, higher employee turnover, missed revenue due to limited capacity, and falling behind competitors already automating. Luckily, <a href="formic.co">Formic</a> makes automation easy. </p> <p>Formic is headed to Indianapolis next for the <a href="https://www.craftbrewersconference.com/">Craft Brewers Conference</a> on April 28th! We’ll see you there. </p> <a href="https://land.formic.co/automate-now-industrial-palletizers">Get Started With Out Automate NOW Industrial Palletizers</a>
  </div>
